{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775892620475,"sessionID":"ses_2848da925ffeSsivYQEgeFrCaj","part":{"id":"prt_d7b72d9e2001r4UCG3u3w0grab","messageID":"msg_d7b72b44b001z9foLRIivRL8qe","sessionID":"ses_2848da925ffeSsivYQEgeFrCaj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_0319a40ddc584462b84ae81d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Specification — AR-042: Docusaurus 文档站框架\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: **Module:** `docs`  \n6: **Language:** TypeScript  \n7: **Size:** M  \n8: **Type:** Docusaurus-based documentation site initialization for agentcube project\n9: \n10: **Base Specs:** (No directly matching specs)\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## Requirements & Scenarios\n15: \n16: ### REQ-042.1: Docusaurus Project Initialization\n17: \n18: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide a Docusaurus v3 project initialized in the `docs/` directory.\n19: \n20: #### Scenario: Initialize Docusaurus project\n21: - **GIVEN** the agentcube repository root\n22: - **WHEN** the documentation site is initialized\n23: - **THEN** it SHALL create a Docusaurus v3 project in the `docs/` directory\n24: \n25: #### Scenario: TypeScript configuration\n26: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus is initialized\n27: - **WHEN** project is set up\n28: - **THEN** it SHALL use TypeScript for configuration files (`docusaurus.config.ts`)\n29: \n30: #### Scenario: Package manager selection\n31: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus CLI runs\n32: - **WHEN** dependencies are installed\n33: - **THEN** it SHALL use the project's existing package manager (npm/pnpm/yarn)\n34: \n35: ---\n36: \n37: ### REQ-042.2: Docusaurus Configuration\n38: \n39: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide a `docusaurus.config.ts` configuration file with agentcube branding and settings.\n40: \n41: #### Scenario: Site title configuration\n42: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` exists\n43: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n44: - **THEN** `title` SHALL be set to \"agentcube\"\n45: \n46: #### Scenario: Site tagline configuration\n47: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` exists\n48: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n49: - **THEN** `tagline` SHALL describe agentcube's purpose\n50: \n51: #### Scenario: Site URL configuration\n52: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` exists\n53: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n54: - **THEN** `url` SHALL be set to project's documentation URL\n55: \n56: #### Scenario: Base URL configuration\n57: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` exists\n58: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n59: - **THEN** `baseUrl` SHALL be set to `/agentcube/`\n60: \n61: #### Scenario: Deployment organization\n62: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` exists\n63: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n64: - **THEN** `organizationName` SHALL be set to appropriate GitHub org\n65: \n66: #### Scenario: Deployment project name\n67: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` exists\n68: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n69: - **THEN** `projectName` SHALL be set to \"agentcube\"\n70: \n71: #### Scenario: Theme configuration\n72: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` exists\n73: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n74: - **THEN** it SHALL configure prism theme for code highlighting\n75: \n76: #### Scenario: Navigation bar configuration\n77: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` exists\n78: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n79: - **THEN** `navbar` SHALL include links to docs, GitHub, and other sections\n80: \n81: #### Scenario: Footer configuration\n82: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` exists\n83: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n84: - **THEN** `footer` SHALL include copyright and relevant links\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: ### REQ-042.3: Documentation Content Structure\n89: \n90: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide a documentation directory structure with initial content.\n91: \n92: #### Scenario: Docs directory exists\n93: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus project is initialized\n94: - **WHEN** file structure is inspected\n95: - **THEN** `docs/` directory SHALL exist for documentation markdown files\n96: \n97: #### Scenario: Introductory documentation\n98: - **GIVEN** `docs/` directory exists\n99: - **WHEN** initial content is created\n100: - **THEN** `docs/intro.md` SHALL provide project introduction\n101: \n102: #### Scenario: Getting started documentation\n103: - **GIVEN** `docs/` directory exists\n104: - **WHEN** initial content is created\n105: - **THEN** `docs/getting-started.md` SHALL provide setup instructions\n106: \n107: #### Scenario: Docs sidebar configuration\n108: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus is configured\n109: - **WHEN** sidebar is evaluated\n110: - **THEN** it SHALL define a sidebar with intro and getting-started sections\n111: \n112: ---\n113: \n114: ### REQ-042.4: Static Assets\n115: \n116: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide a `static/` directory for static assets with branding.\n117: \n118: #### Scenario: Static directory exists\n119: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus project is initialized\n120: - **WHEN** file structure is inspected\n121: - **THEN** `static/` directory SHALL exist\n122: \n123: #### Scenario: Favicon configuration\n124: - **GIVEN** `static/` directory exists\n125: - **WHEN** assets are added\n126: - **THEN** `static/favicon.ico` SHALL be present\n127: \n128: #### Scenario: Logo asset\n129: - **GIVEN** `static/` directory exists\n130: - **WHEN** branding assets are added\n131: - **THEN** `static/img/logo.svg` or `static/img/logo.png` SHALL exist\n132: \n133: #### Scenario: Robots.txt\n134: - **GIVEN** `static/` directory exists\n135: - **WHEN** SEO files are added\n136: - **THEN** `static/robots.txt` SHALL be present\n137: \n138: ---\n139: \n140: ### REQ-042.5: NPM Scripts\n141: \n142: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide NPM scripts in `docs/package.json` for common Docusaurus operations.\n143: \n144: #### Scenario: Start script\n145: - **GIVEN** `docs/package.json` exists\n146: - **WHEN** scripts are inspected\n147: - **THEN** `start` script SHALL run Docusaurus development server\n148: \n149: #### Scenario: Build script\n150: - **GIVEN** `docs/package.json` exists\n151: - **WHEN** scripts are inspected\n152: - **THEN** `build` script SHALL generate production build\n153: \n154: #### Scenario: Serve script\n155: - **GIVEN** `docs/package.json` exists\n156: - **WHEN** scripts are inspected\n157: - **THEN** `serve` script SHALL serve production build locally\n158: \n159: #### Scenario: Deploy script\n160: - **GIVEN** `docs/package.json` exists\n161: - **WHEN** scripts are inspected\n162: - **THEN** `deploy` script SHALL deploy to GitHub Pages\n163: \n164: ---\n165: \n166: ### REQ-042.6: Dependencies\n167: \n168: **Requirement:** The system SHALL specify required Docusaurus dependencies in `package.json`.\n169: \n170: #### Scenario: Core Docusaurus dependency\n171: - **GIVEN** `docs/package.json` exists\n172: - **WHEN** dependencies are inspected\n173: - **THEN** `@docusaurus/core` SHALL be listed as dependency (v3.x)\n174: \n175: #### Scenario: Preset Classic\n176: - **GIVEN** `docs/package.json` exists\n177: - **WHEN** dependencies are inspected\n178: - **THEN** `@docusaurus/preset-classic` SHALL be listed as dependency\n179: \n180: #### Scenario: TypeScript support\n181: - **GIVEN** `docs/package.json` exists\n182: - **WHEN** dependencies are inspected\n183: - **THEN** `@docusaurus/module-type-aliases` and `@docusaurus/tsconfig` SHALL be present\n184: \n185: #### Scenario: React dependencies\n186: - **GIVEN** `docs/package.json` exists\n187: - **WHEN** dependencies are inspected\n188: - **THEN** `react` and `react-dom` SHALL be listed as dependencies\n189: \n190: ---\n191: \n192: ### REQ-042.7: TypeScript Configuration\n193: \n194: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide TypeScript configuration for the docs project.\n195: \n196: #### Scenario: TSConfig file exists\n197: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus project is initialized\n198: - **WHEN** configuration is inspected\n199: - **THEN** `docs/tsconfig.json` SHALL exist\n200: \n201: #### Scenario: Docusaurus TSConfig extends\n202: - **GIVEN** `docs/tsconfig.json` exists\n203: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n204: - **THEN** it SHALL extend `@docusaurus/tsconfig`\n205: \n206: #### Scenario: Module resolution\n207: - **GIVEN** `docs/tsconfig.json` exists\n208: - **WHEN** configuration is evaluated\n209: - **THEN** `moduleResolution` SHALL be set to `bundler` or `node`\n210: \n211: ---\n212: \n213: ### REQ-042.8: Git Ignore Configuration\n214: \n215: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide `.gitignore` for the docs directory.\n216: \n217: #### Scenario: Build output ignored\n218: - **GIVEN** `docs/.gitignore` exists\n219: - **WHEN** gitignore is inspected\n220: - **THEN** `build/` directory SHALL be ignored\n221: \n222: #### Scenario: Node modules ignored\n223: - **GIVEN** `docs/.gitignore` exists\n224: - **WHEN** gitignore is inspected\n225: - **THEN** `node_modules/` SHALL be ignored\n226: \n227: #### Scenario: Docusaurus cache ignored\n228: - **GIVEN** `docs/.gitignore` exists\n229: - **WHEN** gitignore is inspected\n230: - **THEN** `.docusaurus/` SHALL be ignored\n231: \n232: ---\n233: \n234: ### REQ-042.9: Development Server\n235: \n236: **Requirement:** The system SHALL support running Docusaurus development server for local preview.\n237: \n238: #### Scenario: Start development server\n239: - **GIVEN** dependencies are installed\n240: - **WHEN** `npm start` (or equivalent) is executed in `docs/`\n241: - **THEN** Docusaurus dev server SHALL start on `localhost:3000`\n242: \n243: #### Scenario: Hot reload\n244: - **GIVEN** dev server is running\n245: - **WHEN** documentation markdown files are modified\n246: - **THEN** changes SHALL be reflected without manual refresh\n247: \n248: #### Scenario: Build without errors\n249: - **GIVEN** documentation content exists\n250: - **WHEN** `npm run build` is executed\n251: - **THEN** build SHALL complete without errors\n252: \n253: ---\n254: \n255: ### REQ-042.10: README Documentation\n256: \n257: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide a `docs/README.md` with instructions for working with the documentation site.\n258: \n259: #### Scenario: README exists\n260: - **GIVEN** docs directory is initialized\n261: - **WHEN** file structure is inspected\n262: - **THEN** `docs/README.md` SHALL exist\n263: \n264: #### Scenario: Quick start instructions\n265: - **GIVEN** `docs/README.md` exists\n266: - **WHEN** content is inspected\n267: - **THEN** it SHALL include commands to start dev server\n268: \n269: #### Scenario: Build instructions\n270: - **GIVEN** `docs/README.md` exists\n271: - **WHEN** content is inspected\n272: - **THEN** it SHALL include commands to build production site\n273: \n274: #### Scenario: Deployment instructions\n275: - **GIVEN** `docs/README.md` exists\n276: - **WHEN** content is inspected\n277: - **THEN** it SHALL include instructions for deploying to GitHub Pages\n278: \n279: ---\n280: \n281: ## Data Types\n282: \n283: ```typescript\n284: // docusaurus.config.ts structure\n285: interface Config {\n286:   title: string;\n287:   tagline: string;\n288:   url: string;\n289:   baseUrl: string;\n290:   organizationName: string;\n291:   projectName: string;\n292:   presets: [\n293:     '@docusaurus/preset-classic',\n294:     {\n295:       docs: DocsOptions;\n296:       blog: false;\n297:       theme: ThemeOptions;\n298:     }\n299:   ];\n300: }\n301: ```\n302: \n303: ```json\n304: // package.json structure\n305: {\n306:   \"name\": \"agentcube-docs\",\n307:   \"version\": \"0.0.0\",\n308:   \"private\": true,\n309:   \"scripts\": {\n310:     \"start\": \"docusaurus start\",\n311:     \"build\": \"docusaurus build\",\n312:     \"serve\": \"docusaurus serve\",\n313:     \"deploy\": \"docusaurus deploy\"\n314:   },\n315:   \"dependencies\": {\n316:     \"@docusaurus/core\": \"^3.0.0\",\n317:     \"@docusaurus/preset-classic\": \"^3.0.0\",\n318:     \"react\": \"^18.0.0\",\n319:     \"react-dom\": \"^18.0.0\"\n320:   },\n321:   \"devDependencies\": {\n322:     \"@docusaurus/module-type-aliases\": \"^3.0.0\",\n323:     \"@docusaurus/tsconfig\": \"^3.0.0\",\n324:     \"typescript\": \"~5.2.0\"\n325:   }\n326: }\n327: ```\n328: \n329: ---\n330: \n331: ## File Structure\n332: \n333: ```\n334: agentcube/\n335: ├── docs/\n336: │   ├── .gitignore                    # Git ignore for build artifacts\n337: │   ├── README.md                     # Documentation for working with docs\n338: │   ├── package.json                  # NPM dependencies and scripts\n339: │   ├── tsconfig.json                 # TypeScript configuration\n340: │   ├── docusaurus.config.ts          # Docusaurus site configuration\n341: │   ├── sidebars.ts                   # Documentation sidebar configuration\n342: │   ├── docs/\n343: │   │   ├── intro.md                  # Introduction documentation\n344: │   │   └── getting-started.md        # Getting started guide\n345: │   └── static/\n346: │       ├── favicon.ico               # Site favicon\n347: │       ├── robots.txt                # SEO robots file\n348: │       └── img/\n349: │           └── logo.svg              # Project logo\n350: ```\n351: \n352: ---\n353: \n354: ## NPM Scripts\n355: \n356: | Script | Command | Description |\n357: |--------|---------|-------------|\n358: | `start` | `docusaurus start` | Start development server at localhost:3000 |\n359: | `build` | `docusaurus build` | Generate static build into `build/` |\n360: | `serve` | `docusaurus serve` | Serve production build locally |\n361: | `deploy` | `docusaurus deploy` | Deploy to GitHub Pages |\n362: \n363: ---\n364: \n365: ## Configuration Options\n366: \n367: | Option | Purpose | Default | Overridable |\n368: |--------|---------|---------|-------------|\n369: | `title` | Site title | \"agentcube\" | Yes |\n370: | `tagline` | Site description | \"Documentation\" | Yes |\n371: | `url` | Site URL | \"https://your-docusaurus-site.github.io\" | Yes |\n372: | `baseUrl` | Base URL path | \"/agentcube/\" | Yes |\n373: | `organizationName` | GitHub org | \"volcano-sh\" | Yes |\n374: | `projectName` | GitHub repo | \"agentcube\" | Yes |\n375: | `deploymentBranch` | Deploy branch | \"gh-pages\" | Yes |\n376: \n377: ---\n378: \n379: ## Acceptance Checklist\n380: \n381: - [ ] `docs/` — Directory exists with Docusaurus v3 project\n382: - [ ] `docs/package.json` — Contains required Docusaurus dependencies\n383: - [ ] `docs/package.json` — Contains `start`, `build`, `serve`, `deploy` scripts\n384: - [ ] `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` — TypeScript configuration file exists\n385: - [ ] `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` — Configured with agentcube branding\n386: - [ ] `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` — URL and baseUrl properly set\n387: - [ ] `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` — Navbar configured with links\n388: - [ ] `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` — Footer configured\n389: - [ ] `docs/tsconfig.json` — Extends @docusaurus/tsconfig\n390: - [ ] `docs/sidebars.ts` — Sidebar configuration exists\n391: - [ ] `docs/docs/intro.md` — Introduction documentation exists\n392: - [ ] `docs/docs/getting-started.md` — Getting started guide exists\n393: - [ ] `docs/static/` — Static assets directory exists\n394: - [ ] `docs/static/favicon.ico` — Favicon present\n395: - [ ] `docs/static/img/logo.svg` — Logo asset present\n396: - [ ] `docs/static/robots.txt` — SEO file present\n397: - [ ] `docs/.gitignore` — Ignores `build/`, `node_modules/`, `.docusaurus/`\n398: - [ ] `docs/README.md` — Instructions for working with docs\n399: - [ ] `npm start` — Development server starts successfully\n400: - [ ] `npm run build` — Production build completes without errors\n401: - [ ] Dependencies — All required packages installed\n402: \n403: ---\n404: \n405: ## Open Questions\n406: \n407: 1. Should the documentation site be deployed as part of CI/CD automatically on merge to main?\n408: 2. Should i18n (internationalization) be configured from the start?\n409: 3. Should a blog section be enabled for release announcements?\n410: 4. Should Algolia DocSearch be integrated for search functionality?\n411: 5. Should custom CSS/theming be applied for agentcube branding?\n412: 6. Should versioning (docs versioning) be enabled for multiple releases?\n\n(End of file - total 412 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Specification — AR-042: Docusaurus 文档站框架\n\n## Overview\n\n**Module:** `docs`  \n**Language:** TypeScript  \n**Size:** M  \n**Type:** Docusaurus-based documentation site initialization for agentcube project\n\n**Base Specs:** (No directly matching specs)\n\n---\n\n## Requirements & Scenarios\n\n### REQ-042.1: Docusaurus Project Initialization\n\n**Requirement:** The system SHALL provide a Docusaurus v3 project initialized in the `docs/` directory.\n\n#### Scenario: Initialize Docusaurus project","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775892620449,"end":1775892620473}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775892620477,"sessionID":"ses_2848da925ffeSsivYQEgeFrCaj","part":{"id":"prt_d7b72d47c001G03XxvKldyod00","messageID":"msg_d7b72b44b001z9foLRIivRL8qe","sessionID":"ses_2848da925ffeSsivYQEgeFrCaj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_e0ac83cc80884a918f794388","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n2: \n3: - **Module**: docs\n4: - **Language**: TypeScript\n5: - **Size**: M\n6: \n7: ## Summary\n8: \n9: Initialize a Docusaurus-based documentation site framework for the agentcube project.\n\n(End of file - total 9 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n\n- **Module**: docs\n- **Language**: TypeScript\n- **Size**: M\n\n## Summary\n\nInitialize a Docusaurus-based documentation site framework for the agentcube project.","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/spec.md","time":{"start":1775892620443,"end":1775892620476}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775892620481,"sessionID":"ses_2848da925ffeSsivYQEgeFrCaj","part":{"id":"prt_d7b72df8200111J1sYX2KutmSH","messageID":"msg_d7b72b44b001z9foLRIivRL8qe","sessionID":"ses_2848da925ffeSsivYQEgeFrCaj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_acd44f78fee04ffe8ba605d5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-042: Docusaurus 文档站框架\n2: \n3: ## 1. Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube 项目构建基于 Docusaurus 3.x 的现代化文档站点框架，提供统一、可维护、易扩展的技术文档基础设施。\n6: \n7: 本提案针对 AR-042 需求，建立以下核心能力：\n8: \n9: 1. **文档站点基础架构** - 基于 Docusaurus 3.x 的静态站点生成和部署\n10: 2. **技术规范文档化** - 将现有 AR (Architecture Requirement) 文档、设计规范、API 文档整合到统一站点\n11: 3. **多版本支持** - 支持多版本文档并存（如 v0.1.x, v0.2.x 等）\n12: 4. **中英文国际化** - 支持中文和英文文档切换\n13: 5. **搜索和导航** - 集成 Algolia DocSearch 和结构化导航\n14: 6. **CI/CD 集成** - 自动化构建和部署到 GitHub Pages\n15: \n16: 本文档站将作为 AgentCube 项目的官方文档入口，服务于开发者、运维人员和技术决策者。\n17: \n18: ## 2. Scope\n19: \n20: **Module:** `docs/`  \n21: **Language:** TypeScript / Markdown  \n22: **Size:** M\n23: \n24: ### 2.1 In Scope\n25: \n26: | 文档类别 | 目录 | 优先级 | 内容类型 | 状态 |\n27: |----------|------|--------|----------|------|\n28: | **基础文档** | | | | |\n29: | 项目介绍 | `docs/intro/` | P0 | Markdown | 需要创建 |\n30: | 快速开始 | `docs/quickstart/` | P0 | Markdown + 代码示例 | 需要创建 |\n31: | 架构概览 | `docs/architecture/` | P0 | Markdown + 架构图 | 需要创建 |\n32: | **开发文档** | | | | |\n33: | 核心概念 | `docs/concepts/` | P0 | Markdown | 需要创建 |\n34: | CRD 参考 | `docs/crd-reference/` | P0 | Markdown + YAML 示例 | 需要创建 |\n35: | API 参考 | `docs/api-reference/` | P1 | OpenAPI + Markdown | 需要创建 |\n36: | SDK/CLI 使用 | `docs/sdk-cli/` | P0 | Markdown + 代码示例 | 需要创建 |\n37: | **运维文档** | | | | |\n38: | 部署指南 | `docs/deployment/` | P0 | Markdown + Helm 示例 | 需要创建 |\n39: | 配置参考 | `docs/configuration/` | P1 | Markdown + 配置表 | 需要创建 |\n40: | 监控和日志 | `docs/observability/` | P2 | Markdown | 需要创建 |\n41: | 故障排除 | `docs/troubleshooting/` | P2 | Markdown + FAQ | 需要创建 |\n42: | **架构需求** | | | | |\n43: | AR-001 ~ AR-042 | `docs/requirements/` | P1 | Markdown (从现有文档迁移) | 部分已有 |\n44: | **贡献指南** | | | | |\n45: | 开发流程 | `docs/contributing/` | P2 | Markdown | 需要创建 |\n46: | 代码规范 | `docs/style-guide/` | P2 | Markdown | 需要创建 |\n47: \n48: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n49: \n50: - 产品营销页面（由官网负责）\n51: - 社区论坛（由 GitHub Discussions 负责）\n52: - 交互式 API 测试（由 Swagger UI 负责）\n53: - 视频教程（由 YouTube/B 站负责）\n54: - 博客系统（可由 Docusaurus Blog 功能后续扩展）\n55: \n56: ## 3. Current State Analysis\n57: \n58: ### 3.1 现有文档资产\n59: \n60: 当前项目中的文档分散在多个位置：\n61: \n62: | 文档类型 | 位置 | 格式 | 状态 |\n63: |----------|------|------|------|\n64: | 项目说明 | `project.md` | Markdown | 已有 |\n65: | 设计规范 | `design.md` | Markdown | 已有 |\n66: | 增量规范 | `delta-spec.md`, `delta-spec-ar-021.md` 等 | Markdown | 已有 |\n67: | AR 提案 | `changes/AR-*/proposal.md` | Markdown | 分散 |\n68: | 验证报告 | `changes/AR-*/verification-report.md` | Markdown | 分散 |\n69: | 部署文档 | `deployment/*.md` | Markdown | 部分已有 |\n70: | 客户端库文档 | `client-go/*.md` | Markdown | 部分已有 |\n71: | 测试文档 | `test/e2e/README.md` 等 | Markdown | 分散 |\n72: \n73: ### 3.2 Gaps Identified\n74: \n75: 1. **文档分散** - 文档散落在不同目录，缺乏统一入口和导航\n76: 2. **格式不一致** - 不同文档采用不同格式和风格\n77: 3. **版本缺失** - 无法追溯历史版本文档\n78: 4. **搜索困难** - 缺乏全文搜索能力\n79: 5. **无国际化** - 仅支持中文，无法服务国际用户\n80: 6. **部署手动** - 文档更新需要手动操作\n81: 7. **缺少交互** - 代码示例无法直接运行或复制\n82: \n83: ### 3.3 Docusaurus 能力匹配\n84: \n85: | 需求 | Docusaurus 功能 | 满足度 |\n86: |------|----------------|--------|\n87: | 静态站点生成 | Built-in | ✅ 完全满足 |\n88: | Markdown 支持 | MDX (Markdown + JSX) | ✅ 完全满足 |\n89: | 版本控制 | Versioning 插件 | ✅ 完全满足 |\n90: | 国际化 | i18n 插件 | ✅ 完全满足 |\n91: | 搜索 | Algolia DocSearch | ✅ 完全满足 |\n92: | 主题定制 | Swizzle 组件 | ✅ 完全满足 |\n93: | CI/CD | GitHub Actions 集成 | ✅ 完全满足 |\n94: | 代码高亮 | Prism.js / Highlight.js | ✅ 完全满足 |\n95: | 响应式设计 | 内置 | ✅ 完全满足 |\n96: \n97: ## 4. Proposed Changes\n98: \n99: ### 4.1 目录结构\n100: \n101: ```\n102: docs/\n103: ├── README.md                        # 文档站说明\n104: ├── package.json                     # Node.js 依赖\n105: ├── tsconfig.json                    # TypeScript 配置\n106: ├── docusaurus.config.ts             # Docusaurus 主配置\n107: ├── sidebars.ts                      # 侧边栏导航配置\n108: ├── src/\n109: │   ├── components/                  # 自定义 React 组件\n110: │   │   ├── ArchitectureDiagram/\n111: │   │   ├── CRDTable/\n112: │   │   └── CodeExecutor/\n113: │   ├── css/                         # 自定义样式\n114: │   │   └── custom.css\n115: │   ├── pages/                       # 自定义页面\n116: │   │   ├── index.tsx                # 首页\n117: │   │   └── versions.tsx             # 版本列表页\n118: │   └── theme/                       # 主题覆盖\n119: │       └── Footer/\n120: │           └── index.tsx\n121: ├── static/\n122: │   ├── img/                         # 静态图片\n123: │   │   ├── logo.svg\n124: │   │   ├── architecture.png\n125: │   │   └── favicon.ico\n126: │   └── robots.txt\n127: ├── docs/\n128: │   ├── intro/\n129: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n130: │   │   ├── 01-overview.md\n131: │   │   ├── 02-features.md\n132: │   │   └── 03-quickstart.md\n133: │   ├── concepts/\n134: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n135: │   │   ├── 01-agent-runtime.md\n136: │   │   ├── 02-code-interpreter.md\n137: │   │   ├── 03-router.md\n138: │   │   ├── 04-workload-manager.md\n139: │   │   └── 05-sandbox.md\n140: │   ├── crd-reference/\n141: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n142: │   │   ├── agent-runtime.md\n143: │   │   ├── code-interpreter.md\n144: │   │   └── agent-sandbox.md\n145: │   ├── api-reference/\n146: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n147: │   │   ├── overview.md\n148: │   │   ├── router-api.md\n149: │   │   └── workload-manager-api.md\n150: │   ├── sdk-cli/\n151: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n152: │   │   ├── python-sdk.md\n153: │   │   └── cli-toolkit.md\n154: │   ├── deployment/\n155: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n156: │   │   ├── quickstart.md\n157: │   │   ├── helm.md\n158: │   │   ├── kind.md\n159: │   │   └── production.md\n160: │   ├── configuration/\n161: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n162: │   │   ├── environment-variables.md\n163: │   │   └── helm-values.md\n164: │   ├── observability/\n165: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n166: │   │   ├── metrics.md\n167: │   │   └── logging.md\n168: │   ├── troubleshooting/\n169: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n170: │   │   ├── faq.md\n171: │   │   └── common-issues.md\n172: │   ├── requirements/\n173: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n174: │   │   ├── ar-001.md\n175: │   │   ├── ar-002.md\n176: │   │   └── ... (AR-001 ~ AR-042)\n177: │   └── contributing/\n178: │       ├── _category_.json\n179: │       ├── development-guide.md\n180: │       └── style-guide.md\n181: ├── versioned_docs/                   # 版本文档（自动生成）\n182: │   └── version-0.1.x/\n183: ├── versioned_sidebars/               # 版本侧边栏（自动生成）\n184: │   └── version-0.1.x-sidebars.json\n185: └── i18n/                             # 国际化\n186:     ├── zh/                           # 中文（默认）\n187:     │   ├── docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/\n188:     │   │   └── current/\n189:     │   └── docusaurus-theme-classic/\n190:     │       └── footer.json\n191:     └── en/                           # 英文\n192:         ├── docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/\n193:         │   └── current/\n194:         └── docusaurus-theme-classic/\n195:             └── footer.json\n196: ```\n197: \n198: ### 4.2 核心配置\n199: \n200: #### 4.2.1 `docusaurus.config.ts`\n201: \n202: ```typescript\n203: import {themes as prismThemes} from 'prism-react-renderer';\n204: import type {Config} from '@docusaurus/types';\n205: import type * as Preset from '@docusaurus/preset-classic';\n206: \n207: const config: Config = {\n208:   title: 'AgentCube',\n209:   tagline: 'Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agents',\n210:   favicon: 'img/favicon.ico',\n211: \n212:   // Set the production url of your site here\n213:   url: 'https://volcano-sh.github.io',\n214:   baseUrl: '/agentcube/',\n215: \n216:   // GitHub Pages deployment\n217:   organizationName: 'volcano-sh',\n218:   projectName: 'agentcube',\n219: \n220:   onBrokenLinks: 'throw',\n221:   onBrokenMarkdownLinks: 'warn',\n222: \n223:   // Even if you don't use internationalization, you can use this field to set\n224:   // useful metadata like html lang. For example, if your site is Chinese, you\n225:   // may want to replace \"en\" with \"zh-Hans\".\n226:   i18n: {\n227:     defaultLocale: 'zh',\n228:     locales: ['zh', 'en'],\n229:     localeConfigs: {\n230:       zh: {\n231:         htmlLang: 'zh-CN',\n232:         label: '简体中文',\n233:       },\n234:       en: {\n235:         htmlLang: 'en-US',\n236:         label: 'English',\n237:       },\n238:     },\n239:   },\n240: \n241:   presets: [\n242:     [\n243:       'classic',\n244:       {\n245:         docs: {\n246:           sidebarPath: './sidebars.ts',\n247:           // Please change this to your repo.\n248:           // Remove this to remove the \"edit this page\" links.\n249:           editUrl:\n250:             'https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/tree/main/docs/',\n251:           // Versioning\n252:           versions: {\n253:             current: {\n254:               label: 'v0.2.x (Development)',\n255:             },\n256:           },\n257:           // Last update time\n258:           showLastUpdateTime: true,\n259:           showLastUpdateAuthor: true,\n260:         },\n261:         blog: false, // Disable blog for now\n262:         theme: {\n263:           customCss: './src/css/custom.css',\n264:         },\n265:       } satisfies Preset.Options,\n266:     ],\n267:   ],\n268: \n269:   themeConfig: {\n270:     // Replace with your project's social card\n271:     image: 'img/social-card.png',\n272:     navbar: {\n273:       title: 'AgentCube',\n274:       logo: {\n275:         alt: 'AgentCube Logo',\n276:         src: 'img/logo.svg',\n277:       },\n278:       items: [\n279:         {\n280:           type: 'docSidebar',\n281:           sidebarId: 'tutorialSidebar',\n282:           position: 'left',\n283:           label: 'Documentation',\n284:         },\n285:         {\n286:           type: 'docsVersionDropdown',\n287:           position: 'right',\n288:           dropdownActiveClassDisabled: true,\n289:         },\n290:         {\n291:           type: 'localeDropdown',\n292:           position: 'right',\n293:         },\n294:         {\n295:           href: 'https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube',\n296:           label: 'GitHub',\n297:           position: 'right',\n298:         },\n299:       ],\n300:     },\n301:     footer: {\n302:       style: 'dark',\n303:       links: [\n304:         {\n305:           title: 'Docs',\n306:           items: [\n307:             {\n308:               label: 'Quick Start',\n309:               to: '/docs/intro/01-overview',\n310:             },\n311:             {\n312:               label: 'Architecture',\n313:               to: '/docs/architecture',\n314:             },\n315:             {\n316:               label: 'CRD Reference',\n317:               to: '/docs/crd-reference/agent-runtime',\n318:             },\n319:           ],\n320:         },\n321:         {\n322:           title: 'Community',\n323:           items: [\n324:             {\n325:               label: 'GitHub',\n326:               href: 'https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube',\n327:             },\n328:             {\n329:               label: 'Discussions',\n330:               href: 'https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/discussions',\n331:             },\n332:           ],\n333:         },\n334:         {\n335:           title: 'More',\n336:           items: [\n337:             {\n338:               label: 'Volcano',\n339:               href: 'https://volcano.sh/',\n340:             },\n341:           ],\n342:         },\n343:       ],\n344:       copyright: `Copyright © ${new Date().getFullYear()} AgentCube Contributors.`,\n345:     },\n346:     prism: {\n347:       theme: prismThemes.github,\n348:       darkTheme: prismThemes.dracula,\n349:       additionalLanguages: ['bash', 'yaml', 'json', 'go', 'python'],\n350:     },\n351:     // Algolia DocSearch\n352:     algolia: {\n353:       appId: 'YOUR_APP_ID',\n354:       apiKey: 'YOUR_API_KEY',\n355:       indexName: 'agentcube',\n356:       contextualSearch: true,\n357:     },\n358:   } satisfies Preset.ThemeConfig,\n359: \n360:   // Plugins\n361:   plugins: [\n362:     [\n363:       '@docusaurus/plugin-content-docs',\n364:       {\n365:         id: 'requirements',\n366:         path: 'docs/requirements',\n367:         routeBasePath: 'requirements',\n368:         sidebarPath: './sidebars.ts',\n369:       },\n370:     ],\n371:   ],\n372: };\n373: \n374: export default config;\n375: ```\n376: \n377: #### 4.2.2 `sidebars.ts`\n378: \n379: ```typescript\n380: import type {SidebarsConfig} from '@docusaurus/plugin-content-docs';\n381: \n382: const sidebars: SidebarsConfig = {\n383:   tutorialSidebar: [\n384:     {\n385:       type: 'category',\n386:       label: 'Introduction',\n387:       link: {\n388:         type: 'doc',\n389:         id: 'intro/01-overview',\n390:       },\n391:       items: [\n392:         'intro/01-overview',\n393:         'intro/02-features',\n394:         'intro/03-quickstart',\n395:       ],\n396:     },\n397:     {\n398:       type: 'category',\n399:       label: 'Core Concepts',\n400:       link: {\n401:         type: 'doc',\n402:         id: 'concepts/01-agent-runtime',\n403:       },\n404:       items: [\n405:         'concepts/01-agent-runtime',\n406:         'concepts/02-code-interpreter',\n407:         'concepts/03-router',\n408:         'concepts/04-workload-manager',\n409:         'concepts/05-sandbox',\n410:       ],\n411:     },\n412:     {\n413:       type: 'category',\n414:       label: 'CRD Reference',\n415:       link: {\n416:         type: 'doc',\n417:         id: 'crd-reference/agent-runtime',\n418:       },\n419:       items: [\n420:         'crd-reference/agent-runtime',\n421:         'crd-reference/code-interpreter',\n422:         'crd-reference/agent-sandbox',\n423:       ],\n424:     },\n425:     {\n426:       type: 'category',\n427:       label: 'API Reference',\n428:       items: [\n429:         'api-reference/overview',\n430:         'api-reference/router-api',\n431:         'api-reference/workload-manager-api',\n432:       ],\n433:     },\n434:     {\n435:       type: 'category',\n436:       label: 'SDK & CLI',\n437:       items: [\n438:         'sdk-cli/python-sdk',\n439:         'sdk-cli/cli-toolkit',\n440:       ],\n441:     },\n442:     {\n443:       type: 'category',\n444:       label: 'Deployment',\n445:       items: [\n446:         'deployment/quickstart',\n447:         'deployment/helm',\n448:         'deployment/kind',\n449:         'deployment/production',\n450:       ],\n451:     },\n452:     {\n453:       type: 'category',\n454:       label: 'Configuration',\n455:       items: [\n456:         'configuration/environment-variables',\n457:         'configuration/helm-values',\n458:       ],\n459:     },\n460:     {\n461:       type: 'category',\n462:       label: 'Observability',\n463:       items: [\n464:         'observability/metrics',\n465:         'observability/logging',\n466:       ],\n467:     },\n468:     {\n469:       type: 'category',\n470:       label: 'Troubleshooting',\n471:       items: [\n472:         'troubleshooting/faq',\n473:         'troubleshooting/common-issues',\n474:       ],\n475:     },\n476:     {\n477:       type: 'category',\n478:       label: 'Architecture Requirements',\n479:       items: [\n480:         // Auto-generated from AR files\n481:         'requirements/ar-001',\n482:         'requirements/ar-002',\n483:         // ... more ARs\n484:       ],\n485:     },\n486:     {\n487:       type: 'category',\n488:       label: 'Contributing',\n489:       items: [\n490:         'contributing/development-guide',\n491:         'contributing/style-guide',\n492:       ],\n493:     },\n494:   ],\n495: };\n496: \n497: export default sidebars;\n498: ```\n499: \n500: #### 4.2.3 `package.json`\n501: \n502: ```json\n503: {\n504:   \"name\": \"agentcube-docs\",\n505:   \"version\": \"0.2.0\",\n506:   \"private\": true,\n507:   \"scripts\": {\n508:     \"docusaurus\": \"docusaurus\",\n509:     \"start\": \"docusaurus start\",\n510:     \"build\": \"docusaurus build\",\n511:     \"swizzle\": \"docusaurus swizzle\",\n512:     \"deploy\": \"docusaurus deploy\",\n513:     \"clear\": \"docusaurus clear\",\n514:     \"serve\": \"docusaurus serve\",\n515:     \"write-translations\": \"docusaurus write-translations\",\n516:     \"write-heading-ids\": \"docusaurus write-heading-ids\",\n517:     \"typecheck\": \"tsc\"\n518:   },\n519:   \"dependencies\": {\n520:     \"@docusaurus/core\": \"^3.6.0\",\n521:     \"@docusaurus/preset-classic\": \"^3.6.0\",\n522:     \"@mdx-js/react\": \"^3.0.0\",\n523:     \"clsx\": \"^2.1.0\",\n524:     \"prism-react-renderer\": \"^2.3.0\",\n525:     \"react\": \"^18.2.0\",\n526:     \"react-dom\": \"^18.2.0\"\n527:   },\n528:   \"devDependencies\": {\n529:     \"@docusaurus/module-type-aliases\": \"^3.6.0\",\n530:     \"@docusaurus/tsconfig\": \"^3.6.0\",\n531:     \"@docusaurus/types\": \"^3.6.0\",\n532:     \"typescript\": \"~5.3.3\"\n533:   },\n534:   \"browserslist\": {\n535:     \"production\": [\n536:       \">0.5%\",\n537:       \"not dead\",\n538:       \"not op_mini all\"\n539:     ],\n540:     \"development\": [\n541:       \"last 3 chrome version\",\n542:       \"last 3 firefox version\",\n543:       \"last 5 safari version\"\n544:     ]\n545:   },\n546:   \"engines\": {\n547:     \"node\": \">=18.0\"\n548:   }\n549: }\n550: ```\n551: \n552: ### 4.3 自定义组件\n553: \n554: #### 4.3.1 CRD 表格组件 (`src/components/CRDTable/index.tsx`)\n555: \n556: ```typescript\n557: import React from 'react';\n558: import styles from './styles.module.css';\n559: \n560: interface FieldSpec {\n561:   name: string;\n562:   type: string;\n563:   required: boolean;\n564:   description: string;\n565: }\n566: \n567: interface CRDTableProps {\n568:   crdName: string;\n569:   fields: FieldSpec[];\n570: }\n571: \n572: export function CRDTable({crdName, fields}: CRDTableProps) {\n573:   return (\n574:     <div className={styles.crdTable}>\n575:       <h3>{crdName}</h3>\n576:       <table>\n577:         <thead>\n578:           <tr>\n579:             <th>Field</th>\n580:             <th>Type</th>\n581:             <th>Required</th>\n582:             <th>Description</th>\n583:           </tr>\n584:         </thead>\n585:         <tbody>\n586:           {fields.map((field) => (\n587:             <tr key={field.name}>\n588:               <td><code>{field.name}</code></td>\n589:               <td><code>{field.type}</code></td>\n590:               <td>{field.required ? '✅' : '❌'}</td>\n591:               <td>{field.description}</td>\n592:             </tr>\n593:           ))}\n594:         </tbody>\n595:       </table>\n596:     </div>\n597:   );\n598: }\n599: \n600: export default CRDTable;\n601: ```\n602: \n603: #### 4.3.2 架构图组件 (`src/components/ArchitectureDiagram/index.tsx`)\n604: \n605: ```typescript\n606: import React from 'react';\n607: import styles from './styles.module.css';\n608: \n609: interface ArchitectureDiagramProps {\n610:   src: string;\n611:   alt: string;\n612: }\n613: \n614: export function ArchitectureDiagram({src, alt}: ArchitectureDiagramProps) {\n615:   return (\n616:     <div className={styles.diagramContainer}>\n617:       <img src={src} alt={alt} className={styles.diagram} />\n618:     </div>\n619:   );\n620: }\n621: \n622: export default ArchitectureDiagram;\n623: ```\n624: \n625: ### 4.4 示例文档内容\n626: \n627: #### 4.4.1 概述文档 (`docs/intro/01-overview.md`)\n628: \n629: ```markdown\n630: ---\n631: sidebar_label: Overview\n632: title: AgentCube Overview\n633: description: Introduction to AgentCube - Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agents\n634: ---\n635: \n636: # AgentCube Overview\n637: \n638: ## What is AgentCube?\n639: \n640: AgentCube is a **Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform** designed for AI agents. It provides:\n641: \n642: - **Isolated Execution**: Each agent runs in its own sandboxed environment\n643: - **Session Management**: Automatic session binding and lifecycle management\n644: - **Resource Efficiency**: Warm pool mechanism for fast startup and resource reuse\n645: - **Multi-tenant Support**: Namespace isolation and RBAC-based access control\n646: \n647: ## Key Features\n648: \n649: | Feature | Description |\n650: |---------|-------------|\n651: | AgentRuntime | Declarative agent deployment and management |\n652: | CodeInterpreter | Secure code execution with resource limits |\n653: | Router | Intelligent request routing and session affinity |\n654: | WorkloadManager | Kubernetes-native workload orchestration |\n655: \n656: ## Architecture\n657: \n658: ```\n659: ┌──────────────┐\n660: │   Client     │\n661: └──────┬───────┘\n662:        │\n663:        ▼\n664: ┌──────────────┐\n665: │    Router    │◄───────┐\n666: └──────┬───────┘        │\n667:        │                │\n668:        ▼                │\n669: ┌──────────────┐   ┌────┴────┐\n670: │  Workload    │   │  Redis  │\n671: │   Manager    │   │ (Store) │\n672: └──────┬───────┘   └─────────┘\n673:        │\n674:        ▼\n675: ┌──────────────┐\n676: │   Sandbox    │\n677: │     Pods     │\n678: └──────────────┘\n679: ```\n680: \n681: ## Quick Links\n682: \n683: - [Quick Start](./03-quickstart.md) - Get started in 5 minutes\n684: - [Architecture](../architecture) - Deep dive into architecture\n685: - [CRD Reference](../crd-reference/agent-runtime) - API reference\n686: ```\n687: \n688: #### 4.4.2 CRD 参考文档 (`docs/crd-reference/agent-runtime.md`)\n689: \n690: ```markdown\n691: ---\n692: sidebar_label: AgentRuntime\n693: title: AgentRuntime CRD\n694: description: AgentRuntime custom resource definition reference\n695: ---\n696: \n697: # AgentRuntime CRD\n698: \n699: The `AgentRuntime` resource defines an AI agent's runtime configuration.\n700: \n701: ## API Version\n702: \n703: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n704: \n705: ## Kind\n706: \n707: `AgentRuntime`\n708: \n709: ## Example\n710: \n711: ```yaml\n712: apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n713: kind: AgentRuntime\n714: metadata:\n715:   name: echo-agent\n716:   namespace: default\n717:   labels:\n718:     agentcube/expose: \"true\"\n719: spec:\n720:   image: volcanosh/echo-agent:latest\n721:   command: [\"python\", \"-m\", \"echo_agent\"]\n722:   sessionTimeout: \"5m\"\n723:   resources:\n724:     requests:\n725:       cpu: \"0.1\"\n726:       memory: \"64Mi\"\n727:     limits:\n728:       cpu: \"0.5\"\n729:       memory: \"128Mi\"\n730: ```\n731: \n732: ## Specification\n733: \n734: <CRDTable \n735:   crdName=\"AgentRuntimeSpec\"\n736:   fields={[\n737:     {name: \"image\", type: \"string\", required: true, description: \"Container image\"},\n738:     {name: \"command\", type: \"string[]\", required: false, description: \"Container command\"},\n739:     {name: \"sessionTimeout\", type: \"string\", required: false, description: \"Session TTL\"},\n740:     {name: \"resources\", type: \"ResourceRequirements\", required: false, description: \"Resource limits\"},\n741:   ]}\n742: />\n743: \n744: ## Status\n745: \n746: The `status` subresource reflects the current state of the AgentRuntime.\n747: \n748: ```yaml\n749: status:\n750:   ready: true\n751:   backendURL: \"http://echo-agent-svc:8080\"\n752:   phase: Running\n753:   conditions:\n754:     - type: Ready\n755:       status: \"True\"\n756:       lastTransitionTime: \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\"\n757: ```\n758: ```\n759: \n760: ### 4.5 CI/CD 集成\n761: \n762: #### 4.5.1 GitHub Actions Workflow (`.github/workflows/docs.yml`)\n763: \n764: ```yaml\n765: name: Deploy Documentation\n766: \n767: on:\n768:   push:\n769:     branches:\n770:       - main\n771:     paths:\n772:       - 'docs/**'\n773:   workflow_dispatch:\n774: \n775: permissions:\n776:   contents: write\n777: \n778: jobs:\n779:   deploy:\n780:     runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n781:     defaults:\n782:       run:\n783:         working-directory: ./docs\n784:     steps:\n785:       - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n786:       \n787:       - name: Setup Node.js\n788:         uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n789:         with:\n790:           node-version: '18'\n791:           cache: 'npm'\n792:           cache-dependency-path: docs/package-lock.json\n793:       \n794:       - name: Install dependencies\n795:         run: npm ci\n796:       \n797:       - name: Build documentation\n798:         run: npm run build\n799:       \n800:       - name: Deploy to GitHub Pages\n801:         uses: peaceiris/actions-gh-pages@v4\n802:         with:\n803:           github_token: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n804:           publish_dir: ./docs/build\n805:           cname: docs.agentcube.io  # Optional: custom domain\n806: ```\n807: \n808: #### 4.5.2 文档更新检查脚本 (`docs/scripts/check-ar-docs.sh`)\n809: \n810: ```bash\n811: #!/bin/bash\n812: \n813: # Check if all AR proposals have corresponding docs\n814: \n815: DOCS_DIR=\"docs/requirements\"\n816: CHANGES_DIR=\"changes\"\n817: \n818: echo \"Checking AR documentation coverage...\"\n819: \n820: for ar_dir in $CHANGES_DIR/AR-*; do\n821:     ar_name=$(basename $ar_dir)\n822:     proposal=\"$ar_dir/proposal.md\"\n823:     doc_file=\"$DOCS_DIR/$(echo $ar_name | tr '[:upper:]' '[:lower:]').md\"\n824:     \n825:     if [ -f \"$proposal\" ] && [ ! -f \"$doc_file\" ]; then\n826:         echo \"⚠️  Missing doc for $ar_name\"\n827:     fi\n828: done\n829: \n830: echo \"Check complete.\"\n831: ```\n832: \n833: ## 5. Impact Analysis\n834: \n835: ### 5.1 依赖\n836: \n837: | 包/工具 | 用途 | 版本 |\n838: |---------|------|------|\n839: | Node.js | 运行时 | >=18.0 |\n840: | Docusaurus | 文档框架 | 3.6.0+ |\n841: | React | UI 框架 | 18.2.0+ |\n842: | TypeScript | 类型系统 | 5.3.3+ |\n843: | Algolia DocSearch | 搜索服务 | - |\n844: | GitHub Pages | 托管服务 | - |\n845: \n846: ### 5.2 受影响组件\n847: \n848: 1. **现有文档** - 需要迁移和重组到新的目录结构\n849: 2. **CI/CD Pipeline** - 新增文档构建和部署流程\n850: 3. **开发流程** - 新增文档编写和审查环节\n851: \n852: ### 5.3 向后兼容性\n853: \n854: - 现有 Markdown 文档可直接迁移\n855: - 原有文档链接需要重定向配置\n856: - 建议设置 301 重定向避免链接失效\n857: \n858: ### 5.4 风险评估\n859: \n860: | 风险 | 可能性 | 影响 | 缓解措施 |\n861: |------|--------|------|----------|\n862: | Docusaurus 学习曲线 | 中 | 低 | 详细文档和示例 |\n863: | 文档迁移工作量大 | 高 | 中 | 分阶段迁移 |\n864: | Algolia 搜索配置复杂 | 中 | 低 | 使用社区索引 |\n865: | 多语言翻译成本高 | 中 | 中 | 优先中文，逐步翻译 |\n866: | 版本管理复杂 | 低 | 中 | 使用 Docusaurus 版本插件 |\n867: \n868: ## 6. Alternatives Considered\n869: \n870: ### 6.1 方案 A: 使用 MkDocs (不采用)\n871: \n872: **描述**: 使用 Python 生态的 MkDocs + Material 主题\n873: \n874: **优点**:\n875: - Python 技术栈，与 SDK 一致\n876: - Material 主题功能丰富\n877: - 配置简单\n878: \n879: **缺点**:\n880: - 版本控制需要额外插件\n881: - 国际化支持较弱\n882: - 自定义组件能力有限\n883: \n884: **不采用原因**: Docusaurus 在版本控制和国际化方面更成熟\n885: \n886: ### 6.2 方案 B: 使用 Hugo (不采用)\n887: \n888: **描述**: 使用 Go 编写的静态站点生成器 Hugo\n889: \n890: **优点**:\n891: - 构建速度极快\n892: - Go 技术栈，与后端一致\n893: - 主题丰富\n894: \n895: **缺点**:\n896: - Go template 学习曲线\n897: - MDX 支持需要额外配置\n898: - 文档生态较小\n899: \n900: **不采用原因**: Docusaurus 的 React 生态更适合自定义组件开发\n901: \n902: ### 6.3 方案 C: 使用 GitBook (不采用)\n903: \n904: **描述**: 使用 SaaS 服务 GitBook\n905: \n906: **优点**:\n907: - 开箱即用\n908: - 协作功能强大\n909: - 无需维护基础设施\n910: \n911: **缺点**:\n912: - 付费服务\n913: - 自定义能力有限\n914: - 数据不在自己控制下\n915: \n916: **不采用原因**: 开源项目应使用开源工具，且需要完全控制\n917: \n918: ### 6.4 方案 D: 使用 VitePress (不采用)\n919: \n920: **描述**: 使用 Vue 生态的 VitePress\n921: \n922: **优点**:\n923: - 构建速度快\n924: - Vue 3 生态\n925: - 配置简洁\n926: \n927: **缺点**:\n928: - 版本控制需要额外工作\n929: - 企业采用案例较少\n930: - 插件生态不如 Docusaurus\n931: \n932: **不采用原因**: Docusaurus 在文档站点领域更成熟\n933: \n934: ## 7. Implementation Plan\n935: \n936: ### Phase 1: 基础框架搭建 (4h)\n937: ```\n938: - [ ] 创建 docs/ 目录结构\n939: - [ ] 初始化 Docusaurus 项目\n940: - [ ] 配置 docusaurus.config.ts\n941: - [ ] 配置 sidebars.ts\n942: - [ ] 设置 package.json 和 TypeScript\n943: - [ ] 创建基础首页\n944: ```\n945: \n946: ### Phase 2: 核心文档创建 (8h)\n947: ```\n948: - [ ] 编写 Introduction 文档\n949: - [ ] 编写 Core Concepts 文档\n950: - [ ] 编写 CRD Reference 文档\n951: - [ ] 编写 Deployment 文档\n952: - [ ] 迁移现有 AR 文档\n953: ```\n954: \n955: ### Phase 3: 自定义组件开发 (4h)\n956: ```\n957: - [ ] 开发 CRDTable 组件\n958: - [ ] 开发 ArchitectureDiagram 组件\n959: - [ ] 开发 CodeExecutor 组件（可选）\n960: - [ ] 配置自定义 CSS\n961: ```\n962: \n963: ### Phase 4: 国际化配置 (3h)\n964: ```\n965: - [ ] 配置 i18n 插件\n966: - [ ] 创建英文翻译骨架\n967: - [ ] 配置语言切换器\n968: - [ ] 翻译核心页面（首页、快速开始）\n969: ```\n970: \n971: ### Phase 5: CI/CD 集成 (3h)\n972: ```\n973: - [ ] 配置 GitHub Actions\n974: - [ ] 设置 GitHub Pages 部署\n975: - [ ] 配置自定义域名（可选）\n976: - [ ] 配置 Algolia DocSearch\n977: ```\n978: \n979: ### Phase 6: 测试和验收 (2h)\n980: ```\n981: - [ ] 本地构建测试\n982: - [ ] 移动端响应测试\n983: - [ ] 链接检查\n984: - [ ] 性能优化\n985: ```\n986: \n987: **总预估时间**: 24 小时\n988: \n989: ## 8. Acceptance Criteria\n990: \n991: - [ ] Docusaurus 站点可以本地启动 (`npm start`)\n992: - [ ] 所有核心文档类别有内容（Introduction, Concepts, CRD Reference, Deployment）\n993: - [ ] 至少 5 个 AR 文档迁移完成\n994: - [ ] 侧边栏导航结构清晰\n995: - [ ] 国际化切换正常工作\n996: - [ ] GitHub Actions 自动部署成功\n997: - [ ] 移动端显示正常\n998: - [ ] 搜索功能可用（Algolia 或本地搜索）\n999: - [ ] 自定义组件（CRDTable）可用\n1000: - [ ] 文档构建时间 < 2 分钟\n1001: \n1002: ## 9. Success Criteria\n1003: \n1004: 1. ✅ 文档站成功部署并可访问\n1005: 2. ✅ 所有核心文档完整且准确\n1006: 3. ✅ 导航和搜索体验良好\n1007: 4. ✅ 多语言切换正常\n1008: 5. ✅ CI/CD 自动化运行\n1009: 6. ✅ 新成员可以参考文档快速上手\n1010: 7. ✅ 文档更新流程顺畅\n1011: \n1012: ## 10. Dependencies\n1013: \n1014: - Node.js 18+\n1015: - npm 或 yarn\n1016: - GitHub Pages 访问权限\n1017: - Algolia DocSearch 账号（可选）\n1018: \n1019: ## 11. References\n1020: \n1021: - [Docusaurus 官方文档](https://docusaurus.io/)\n1022: - [project.md](../../project.md) - 项目上下文\n1023: - [design.md](../../design.md) - 设计规范\n1024: - `changes/AR-*/proposal.md` - 架构需求文档\n1025: - [Volcano 文档](https://volcano.sh/docs/) - 参考文档风格\n1026: \n1027: (End of file - total 652 lines)\n\n(End of file - total 1027 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-042: Docusaurus 文档站框架\n\n## 1. Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube 项目构建基于 Docusaurus 3.x 的现代化文档站点框架，提供统一、可维护、易扩展的技术文档基础设施。\n\n本提案针对 AR-042 需求，建立以下核心能力：\n\n1. **文档站点基础架构** - 基于 Docusaurus 3.x 的静态站点生成和部署\n2. **技术规范文档化** - 将现有 AR (Architecture Requirement) 文档、设计规范、API 文档整合到统一站点\n3. **多版本支持** - 支持多版本文档并存（如 v0.1.x, v0.2.x 等）\n4. **中英文国际化** - 支持中文和英文文档切换\n5. **搜索和导航** - 集成 Algolia DocSearch 和结构化导航\n6. **CI/CD 集成** - 自动化构建和部署到 GitHub Pages\n\n本文档站将作为 AgentCube 项目的官方文档入口，服务于开发者、运维人员和技术决策者。\n\n## 2. Scope\n\n**Module:** `docs/`  ","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775892620451,"end":1775892620477}}}}
